{"tid":293950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴RoadShow 6月底停播！電視將主要提供乘客資訊","createTime":"2017-06-22T14:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T15:41:11.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95dfad24ac7c3a6c0896bf0798f9b03b14aba022","tid":293950,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170622/large/1498097895_5ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170622%2Flarge%2F1498097895_5ede.jpg&h=ea865912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴宣佈，其巴士流動多媒體現時的廣告服務代理權，將於6月30日屆滿，由7月起，車廂內的顯示屏幕將會主要用作提供乘客資訊，意味大家熟悉的「楊校長」、「宿便Jacky」將在巴士車廂消失。<br />\n<br />\nRoadShow在2000年12月起在九巴內啟播，當中製作不少節目，如《救亡16度》、《RoadShow紅人館》等。當中播放不少廣告，高峰期曾在2013年賺1.05億元，惟近年廣告數量減少，乘客經常看到重複廣告，亦曾經被人投訴其聲量太高。<br />\n九巴今日為新款紅色巴士舉行傳媒預覽時，提到RoadShow完約後，九巴現有電視螢幕將會改為播放乘客實用資訊及生活資訊。"},{"pid":"df2865283d8094593b49cd1dfcc5a989bf8ab298","tid":293950,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"Rainbow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55d3439228ed4ea9324e87922610d4dbe74a04a","tid":293950,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"鬼咩 玩手機啦"},{"pid":"770b90cdd5cc245b9f3bf7daa3045b86229b88bf","tid":293950,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5UchV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5UchV.jpg&h=ef7a908b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f9e16e40c64a64eea4280d708d5bdb0fd05a9fe","tid":293950,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"Jacky便秘左咁多年終於屙到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}